---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Schedule Free Consultation | Restaurant Technology Consulting" 
  description="Book a free 30-minute consultation to discuss your restaurant's technology needs. No sales pitch‚Äîjust honest advice about POS integration, online ordering, and tech optimization."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          Schedule Your Free Consultation
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
          Let's discuss your restaurant's technology challenges and identify opportunities for savings and growth. 
          No pressure, no sales pitch‚Äîjust honest advice.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-primary-100">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">‚è±Ô∏è</div>
            <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">30 Minutes</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Quick & focused</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-primary-100">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">üí∞</div>
            <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">100% Free</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">No strings attached</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-primary-100">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-2">üé•</div>
            <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Video Call</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">From anywhere</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Calendly Embed -->
  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Calendly inline widget begin -->
      <div class="calendly-inline-widget" data-url="https://calendly.com/lukepitstick06/30min?hide_event_type_details=1&hide_gdpr_banner=1" style="min-width:320px;height:700px;"></div>
      <script is:inline type="text/javascript" src="https://assets.calendly.com/assets/external/widget.js" async></script>
      <!-- Calendly inline widget end -->
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What to Expect -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">What to Expect on the Call</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-primary-100 flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl mr-6">
            1
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Quick Introduction</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">We'll learn about your restaurant, current operations, and what brought you here today.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-primary-100 flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl mr-6">
            2
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Review Current Tech Stack</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">We'll discuss your current systems: POS, inventory, scheduling, online ordering, accounting.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-primary-100 flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl mr-6">
            3
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Identify Pain Points</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">What's frustrating? What's costing you time or money? What manual processes could be automated?</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-primary-100 flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl mr-6">
            4
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Spot Quick Wins</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">We'll identify 1-2 immediate opportunities for savings or improvement, even if you don't hire us.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border border-primary-100 flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl mr-6">
            5
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Discuss Next Steps</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700">If there's a fit, we'll talk about a tech audit or project scope. If not, we'll point you in the right direction.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">Common Questions</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-primary-100">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is this really free?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Yes! The consultation is 100% free with no obligation. We want to understand your needs before discussing any paid services.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-primary-100">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What should I prepare?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Just come ready to talk about your current systems and challenges. If you have login info or vendor contracts handy, that's helpful but not required.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-primary-100">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Will you try to sell me something?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">No pressure sales. If we can help, we'll explain how. If we're not the right fit, we'll tell you that too and point you in the right direction.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-primary-100">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What if I need to reschedule?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">No problem! You can reschedule or cancel anytime via the confirmation email you'll receive after booking.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Alternative Contact -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Prefer to Email Instead?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
        No problem! Drop us a line and we'll respond within 24 hours.
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:hello@megabite.consulting" class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-500 to-primary-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-lg font-semibold hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105">
        Email: hello@megabite.consulting
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
